OL,6,FFormer Health Secretary Matt Hancock
OL,7,Flibelled parliamentary candidate
OL,8,FAndrew Bridgen to a "devastating
OL,9,Fextent" by accusing him of
OL,10,Fantisemitism on social media, the High
OL,11,FCourt has been told.
OL,13,FThe former North West Leicestershire
OL,14,FMP is bringing a libel case against Mr
OL,15,FHancock over a post on X, formerly
OL,16,FTwitter, last year, after Mr Bridgen
OL,17,Fposted a comment about Covid-19
OL,18,Fvaccines.
