OL,6,FThe High Court in London previously
OL,7,Fheard that on January 11th 2023, Mr
OL,8,FBridgen shared a link to an article
OL,9,F"concerning data about deaths and
OL,10,Fother adverse reactions linked to
OL,11,FCovid vaccines", and stated: "As one
OL,12,Fconsultant cardiologist said to me,
OL,13,Fthis is the biggest crime against
OL,14,Fhumanity since the Holocaust."
