OL,3,CHigh Court told Matt Hancock libelled
OL,4,CAndrew Bridgen to 'devastating extent'
OL,6,FHe said: "We say that the gravity of
OL,7,Fwhat was said, even on the defendant's
OL,8,Fmeaning, was very serious indeed.
OL,10,F"A libel about antisemitism is a
OL,11,Fparticularly serious libel."
OL,13,FHe continued: "We live in a society
OL,14,Fwhere racism is not just undesirable,
OL,15,Fit is legislated to be illegal... and
OL,16,Fantisemitism as a very specific form
OL,17,Fof racism, just as bad as any other
OL,18,Fform of racism."
