OL,3,CHigh Court told Matt Hancock libelled
OL,4,CAndrew Bridgen to 'devastating extent'
OL,6,FHe added: "If somebody says you are
OL,7,Fantisemitic, everyone knows what that
OL,8,Fmeans. It is just very, very damaging."
OL,10,FMr Newman said the post meant Mr
OL,11,FBridgen "is an antisemite", while
OL,12,Flawyers for Mr Hancock told the court
OL,13,Fit meant Mr Bridgen had "disseminated
OL,14,Fviews that were antisemitic in nature".
OL,16,FMr Bridgen previously told the court
OL,17,Fthat "every person reading the tweet
OL,18,Fknew it was about me", that it was
OL,19,F"seriously defamatory and untrue" and
OL,20,Fintended to cause "grievous harm" to
OL,21,Fhis reputation.
