OL,6,FHe also said he wished to "clear his
OL,7,Fname" after the "malicious" post.
OL,9,FMr Hancock has previously called the
OL,10,Fcase "absurd" and labelled Mr
OL,11,FBridgen's claims "ridiculous".
OL,13,FIn written submissions, Aidan Eardley
OL,14,FKC for Mr Hancock, said that only
